QuestData.Title: Iyu
QuestData.Description: There is a genesaur here!$b$bIt wants its artifact back.$b$bKaz and Draka are fighting it now on the surface but they need you. Draka said I could fire the big gun. So I will stay here and do that.
QuestData.RewardText: It was an honor to fight by your side today, commander.
